1.title: Thomas Middleditch

episode of.title: Middle of the Night Show (TV Series 2015– )

1.plot: Murph and the crew wake up Silicon Valley star Thomas Middleditch and force him to host a talk show with no preparation. Thomas visits a luxury dog hotel and competes against Murph in an epic Times Square manhunt.

episode of.title: Middle of the Night Show (TV Series 2015– )

Jordin meets an imposter, interviews Elmo, and competes against Murph in a singing competition.We call it a night with a surprising pizza game, Remix the Night, and a very awkward group photo.

3.title: The Miz

episode of.title: Middle of the Night Show (TV Series 2015– )

3.plot: Murph and the crew wake up WWE superstar The Miz and force him to host a talk show with no preparation. The Miz betrays an old friend, samples extreme hot sauce, and battles Murph in a bizarre food fight. Meanwhile, Anu settles a daunting restaurant bill, and Murph joins forces with world eating champion Kobayashi in order to shut down a hot dog stand. We bring it home with Remix the Night and a trash talk montage with the Miz.

imdb.plot outline: Middle of the Night Show is a fast-paced re-imagining of the late-night comedy talk show that brings it out of the studio and onto the streets of New York City. Each night the show's crew and live band crash the bedroom of an unsuspecting celebrity who is forced to host a talk show on the spot without any preparation and on very little sleep. College Humor's Brian Murphy serves as the celebrity's co-host and guide throughout the evening.
